{"name": "lefaso-net-scraper", "metadata": {"name": "lefaso-net-scraper", "version": "0.4.0", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13"], "home_page": "https://github.com/abdoulfataoh/lefaso-net-scraper", "license": null, "documentation_url": "https://github.com/abdoulfataoh/lefaso-net-scraper/wiki", "dependencies": ["environs", "beautifulsoup4", "requests", "aiohttp", "unidecode"], "summary": "The ultimate library for data scientist to scrape data from https://www.lefaso.net", "upload_time": 1734526297}, "documentation": ["## lefaso-net-scraper\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/lefaso-net-scraper/\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/abdoulfataoh/lefaso-net-scraper/master/docs/icon.png\" style=\"width:60px;height:60px;\"></a>\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://badge.fury.io/py/lefaso-net-scraper\"><img src=\"https://badge.fury.io/py/lefaso-net-scraper.svg\" alt=\"PyPI version\"></a>\n    <a href=\"https://pepy.tech/project/lefaso-net-scraper\"><img src=\"https://static.pepy.tech/badge/lefaso-net-scraper\"></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/abdoulfataoh/lefaso-net-scraper\"><img src=\"https://github.com/abdoulfataoh/lefaso-net-scraper/actions/workflows/test.yaml/badge.svg\"></a> <br>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/abdoulfataoh/lefaso-net-scraper\"><img src=\"https://github.com/abdoulfataoh/lefaso-net-scraper/actions/workflows/publish.yaml/badge.svg\"></a>\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n### Description\nlefaso-net-scraper is a robust and versatile Python library designed to efficiently extract articles from the popular online news source in Burkina Faso,  [www.lefaso.net](https://www.lefaso.net). This powerful scraping tool allows users to effortlessly collect article content and user comments on lefaso.net.\n\n\n\n### Important\n  > This scraper, like other scrapers, is based on the structure of the target website. Changes to the website's structure can affect the scraper. We use automated workflows to detect these issues frequently, but we cannot catch all of them. Please report any issues you encounter and use the latest version.\n\n### JSON/dictionary Fields\n\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n| Field                  | Description                                          |\n|------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|\n| `article_topic`         | Category or subject of the article.                  |\n| `article_title`         | The main headline or title of the article.           |\n| `article_published_date`| Date when the article was published.                 |\n| `article_origin`        | Source or platform where the article was published.  |\n| `article_url`           | Web link to the article.                             |\n| `article_content`       | Full text or body of the article.                    |\n| `article_comments`      | Feedback or responses from readers.                  |\n\n</div>\n\n### Installation\n\n- Using pip\n\n```bash\npip install --upgrade  lefaso-net-scraper\n\n# For jupiter support\npip install --upgrade  lefaso-net-scraper[notebook]\n```\n\n- Using poetry\n\n```bash\npoetry add lefaso-net-scraper\n\n# For jupiter support\npoetry add lefaso-net-scraper[notebook]\n```\n\n### Usage\n\n  \n```python\n# coding: utf-8\n\nfrom lefaso_net_scraper import LefasoNetScraper\n\nsection_url = 'https://lefaso.net/spip.php?rubrique473'\nscraper = LefasoNetScraper(section_url)\ndata = scraper.run()\n```\n\n- Settings Pagination range\n\n```python\n# coding: utf-8\n\nfrom lefaso_net_scraper import LefasoNetScraper\n\nsection_url = 'https://lefaso.net/spip.php?rubrique473'\nscraper = LefasoNetScraper(section_url)\nscraper.set_pagination_range(start=20, stop=100)\ndata = scraper.run()\n```\n\n- Save data to csv\n\n```python\n\n# coding: utf-8\n\nfrom lefaso_net_scraper import LefasoNetScraper\nimport pandas as pd\n\nsection_url = 'https://lefaso.net/spip.php?rubrique473'\nscraper = LefasoNetScraper(section_url)\ndata = scraper.run()\ndf = pd.DataFrame.from_records(data)\ndf.to_csv('path/to/df.csv')\n```\n\n<p align=\"center\">We \u2764 open source</p>\n"], "modules": [{"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.lefaso", "documentation": ["coding: utf-8"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.lefaso.Article", "xref": {"fqname": "lefaso_net_scraper.lefaso.scraper.Article", "project": null}}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.lefaso.LefasoNetScraper", "xref": {"fqname": "lefaso_net_scraper.lefaso.scraper.LefasoNetScraper", "project": null}}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.lefaso.LefasoNetUrlError", "xref": {"fqname": "lefaso_net_scraper.lefaso.scraper.LefasoNetUrlError", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper", "documentation": ["coding: utf-8"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.LefasoNetScraper", "xref": {"fqname": "lefaso_net_scraper.lefaso.scraper.LefasoNetScraper", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.settings", "documentation": ["coding: utf-8"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.settings.env", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.settings.LAFASO_URL", "type": null, "documentation": ["noqa: E501"]}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.settings.LEFASO_PAGINATION_STEP", "type": null, "documentation": ["noqa: E501"]}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.settings.LEFASO_ARTICLES_CONTAINER", "type": null, "documentation": ["noqa: E501"]}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.settings.LEFASO_ARTICLE_SELECTOR", "type": null, "documentation": ["noqa: E501"]}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.settings.LEFASO_PAGINATION_TEMPLATE", "type": null, "documentation": ["noqa: E501"]}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "lefaso_net_scraper.lefaso.scrape